Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等...等一等...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么了?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.10,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这里太亮了，我们能把灯调暗一点吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.52,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我觉得很害羞
