Dialogue: 2,0:33:32.10,0:33:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你们男人总是这样...
Dialogue: 2,0:33:39.17,0:33:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我也想好好学习一下
Dialogue: 2,0:33:47.85,0:33:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}成功了！！
Dialogue: 2,0:34:00.50,0:34:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以，上次我们做的时候，并不是很顺利...
Dialogue: 2,0:34:06.30,0:34:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这次我为了让小南开心，学了很多东西...
Dialogue: 2,0:34:19.57,0:34:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我一定会让小南感觉很舒服
Dialogue: 2,0:34:37.60,0:34:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要疯狂舔你的茂密的小穴!!!
Dialogue: 2,0:34:43.40,0:34:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那么...我来了...
Dialogue: 2,0:34:46.47,0:34:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好的
Dialogue: 2,0:35:49.27,0:35:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}下一步，加藤鹰之手！！！
Dialogue: 2,0:35:54.65,0:35:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我还能做更多吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:58.30,0:35:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}更多...
Dialogue: 2,0:36:00.17,0:36:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}（嗯）
Dialogue: 2,0:36:50.15,0:36:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要不....今...今天，我们就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 2,0:36:54.87,0:36:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失败了！！！
Dialogue: 2,0:37:32.90,0:37:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了让你有更好的感觉，把你的性欲分开，一半分享给你的女朋友。
Dialogue: 2,0:37:42.32,0:37:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为什么这么好吃啊
Dialogue: 2,0:37:48.00,0:37:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}鸡巴真好吃啊
Dialogue: 2,0:37:55.50,0:37:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等等，为什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:57.83,0:37:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}停手啊
Dialogue: 2,0:38:00.45,0:38:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哈？为什么要停止啊？我想吮吸鸡巴啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:38:07.91,0:38:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}躺下来让我好好吮吸鸡巴
Dialogue: 2,0:38:16.75,0:38:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}住手，我不要啊
Dialogue: 2,0:38:22.25,0:38:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}鸡巴好美味啊！！
Dialogue: 2,0:38:27.80,0:38:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}停...停手啊...
Dialogue: 2,0:38:42.55,0:38:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不要啊...停...停手啊...
Dialogue: 2,0:38:47.55,0:38:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好美味啊！！
Dialogue: 2,0:38:49.54,0:38:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要这根鸡巴！！！
Dialogue: 2,0:38:57.77,0:39:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要我继续吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:39:02.40,0:39:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要啊...
Dialogue: 2,0:39:11.17,0:39:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}停手啊！等一等...
Dialogue: 2,0:39:15.70,0:39:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等等...停下啊!
Dialogue: 2,0:39:20.66,0:39:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}停下？但我现在超级有感觉啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:39:27.80,0:39:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要它...
Dialogue: 2,0:39:29.57,0:39:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要吞了它...
Dialogue: 2,0:39:31.72,0:39:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等等...不要啊...
Dialogue: 2,0:39:33.45,0:39:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等一等...你好恐怖啊！！！
Dialogue: 2,0:39:45.12,0:39:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好有感觉啊！！
Dialogue: 2,0:39:50.05,0:39:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}停手啊...
Dialogue: 2,0:39:54.00,0:39:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这是怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: 2,0:40:01.67,0:40:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等等，你好可怕啊！！
Dialogue: 2,0:40:09.52,0:40:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}鸡巴好美味啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:40:23.85,0:40:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要啊...你好可怕啊！！
Dialogue: 2,0:40:31.80,0:40:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}鸡巴变得好硬啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:40:43.80,0:40:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}鸡巴都硬成这样了，不想要吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:40:49.95,0:40:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想我给你口交吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:26.65,0:41:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好好吃啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:41:39.72,0:41:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}停下啊...
Dialogue: 2,0:41:47.85,0:41:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要啊...
Dialogue: 2,0:41:53.60,0:41:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要我舔蛋蛋吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:56.61,0:42:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想吗？美味的蛋蛋！
