Dialogue: 2,0:45:49.72,0:45:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你很舒服，是吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:52.83,0:45:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等等，不行了...啊...等一等...
