Dialogue: 2,1:00:32.62,1:00:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小穴湿透了
Dialogue: 2,1:00:41.55,1:00:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒，好舒服啊。
Dialogue: 2,1:00:55.30,1:00:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小穴好兴奋啊
Dialogue: 2,1:01:03.97,1:01:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还想要更多吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:01:09.30,1:01:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还想做更多刺激的事情吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:01:12.07,1:01:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}（不要了）
Dialogue: 2,1:01:13.55,1:01:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不行！
Dialogue: 2,1:01:16.17,1:01:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小穴还没有舒服够
Dialogue: 2,1:01:20.83,1:01:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}肉棒的工作还没有完成哦
Dialogue: 2,1:01:27.67,1:01:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小穴还要得到更多哦
Dialogue: 2,1:01:34.16,1:01:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要把肉棒放进小穴了哦
Dialogue: 2,1:01:52.52,1:01:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}肉棒进去了哦
Dialogue: 2,1:02:01.40,1:02:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不行，手拿开。
Dialogue: 2,1:02:03.42,1:02:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}其实你想这样做的吧
Dialogue: 2,1:02:18.15,1:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊，好深。
Dialogue: 2,1:02:20.40,1:02:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你喜欢这感觉的吧
Dialogue: 2,1:02:32.52,1:02:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒啊
Dialogue: 2,1:02:36.35,1:02:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}能看到小穴被插的样子吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:02:55.82,1:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很舒服的吧?
Dialogue: 2,1:03:05.67,1:03:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢这样的感觉吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:03:21.05,1:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊，顶到深处了。
Dialogue: 2,1:03:27.85,1:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}其实你想我这样做的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:03:31.93,1:03:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}（不要）
Dialogue: 2,1:03:33.93,1:03:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不行！
Dialogue: 2,1:03:59.10,1:04:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}其实肉棒还想要更多的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:02.77,1:04:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这里...
Dialogue: 2,1:04:05.00,1:04:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这里想要我捏的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:07.85,1:04:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被捏的很有感觉吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:12.95,1:04:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}其实，想要我动的更多吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:27.75,1:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这个姿势更刺激的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:39.72,1:04:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢看我吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:05:00.33,1:05:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你为什么在发抖?
Dialogue: 2,1:05:06.33,1:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什么？你还没有兴奋吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:05:19.80,1:05:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要告诉我你已经满足了
Dialogue: 2,1:05:26.37,1:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快看
Dialogue: 2,1:05:28.00,1:05:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}肉棒插进小穴了哦
Dialogue: 2,1:06:01.50,1:06:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你喜欢看我的屁股吗?
Dialogue: 2,1:06:39.87,1:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}舒服吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:06:44.70,1:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真的吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:06:46.40,1:06:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不觉得这样很刺激吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:06:51.70,1:06:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好厉害的肉棒
Dialogue: 2,1:07:18.07,1:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你一定很有感觉的！
Dialogue: 2,1:07:21.50,1:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我敢说你一定很有感觉的吧
Dialogue: 2,1:07:25.30,1:07:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我说对了吧
Dialogue: 2,1:07:30.45,1:07:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}更多...我还要更多...
Dialogue: 2,1:08:03.40,1:08:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要换个姿势吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:08:10.97,1:08:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不想摸我的奶子吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:08:21.90,1:08:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:08:24.35,1:08:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好舒服！
Dialogue: 2,1:08:26.40,1:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}摸的舒服吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:08:30.22,1:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你很喜欢这样的吧
Dialogue: 2,1:08:54.82,1:08:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好舒服！
Dialogue: 2,1:09:04.72,1:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你很喜欢我的奶子吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:09:20.27,1:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就是这样！
Dialogue: 2,1:09:25.67,1:09:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:09:29.55,1:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}更多...继续...我还要更多...
Dialogue: 2,1:09:34.02,1:09:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你也很舒服的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:10:04.05,1:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:10:05.97,1:10:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}继续...继续啊...
Dialogue: 2,1:10:10.22,1:10:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我受不了了！
Dialogue: 2,1:10:13.87,1:10:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}精液！把你的精液射给我！
Dialogue: 2,1:10:27.97,1:10:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}射了！
Dialogue: 2,1:10:33.17,1:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊...好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:10:39.40,1:10:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你坚持不住了呀。
Dialogue: 2,1:10:42.85,1:10:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}精液好好吃哦
Dialogue: 2,1:11:17.52,1:11:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你这什么表情啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:11:21.30,1:11:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我期待了这么久
Dialogue: 2,1:11:25.02,1:11:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我们下次再做的时候，会让你的肉棒感觉更好哦。
Dialogue: 2,1:11:33.22,1:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我女朋友的性欲越来越旺盛了...
Dialogue: 2,1:12:15.50,1:12:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我可以让你成为我的宠物吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:12:20.40,1:12:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你什么时候开始变成这样了?
Dialogue: 2,1:12:23.27,1:12:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你终于醒了啊
Dialogue: 2,1:12:27.67,1:12:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你喜欢我淫荡的样子吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:12:38.17,1:12:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我过来咯
Dialogue: 2,1:12:44.05,1:12:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我让你兴奋了吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:12:52.33,1:12:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你感觉舒服吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:12:59.85,1:13:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,1:13:05.90,1:13:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这样会更好吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:13:09.47,1:13:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还是你想要...我的小穴这样做?
Dialogue: 2,1:13:23.95,1:13:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还是想要我的屁股这样做？
Dialogue: 2,1:13:33.90,1:13:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}它怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,1:13:36.52,1:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}屁股的味道好吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:13:43.83,1:13:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好好忍耐它...好好品尝它...
Dialogue: 2,1:13:55.22,1:13:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}继续...好好品尝我的屁股...
Dialogue: 2,1:14:11.17,1:14:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,1:14:14.02,1:14:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你很兴奋吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:14:27.16,1:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你真是个变态！
Dialogue: 2,1:14:31.17,1:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要换点别的吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:14:33.12,1:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要我的小穴吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:14:36.72,1:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我的小穴...
Dialogue: 2,1:14:40.15,1:14:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小穴闻起来怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,1:14:47.05,1:14:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}到这里来
Dialogue: 2,1:15:00.70,1:15:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小穴很美味的吧
Dialogue: 2,1:15:09.16,1:15:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我的小穴是什么味道呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:15:23.82,1:15:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还要更多...
Dialogue: 2,1:15:37.27,1:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}做的很好哦
Dialogue: 2,1:15:44.33,1:15:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你现在想要做什么呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:15:52.83,1:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的肉棒还不变硬吗?
Dialogue: 2,1:15:59.66,1:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你还很软啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:16:06.45,1:16:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}现在让我们玩点更开心的吧
Dialogue: 2,1:16:10.15,1:16:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 2,1:16:25.36,1:16:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还想要更多的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:16:59.70,1:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为什么你的项链是个肉棒...
Dialogue: 2,1:17:04.17,1:17:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}它很好看哦
Dialogue: 2,1:17:19.25,1:17:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看你的表情...
Dialogue: 2,1:17:21.82,1:17:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很兴奋了吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:17:26.10,1:17:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不是？
Dialogue: 2,1:17:28.25,1:17:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天我是不会放过你的
Dialogue: 2,1:17:40.97,1:17:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看你这满脸舒服的样子
Dialogue: 2,1:17:50.66,1:17:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你喜欢这样吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:18:06.47,1:18:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}说不要，为什么肉棒变得硬邦邦了？
Dialogue: 2,1:18:12.17,1:18:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明明自己就很想要嘛
Dialogue: 2,1:18:18.97,1:18:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢这样？
Dialogue: 2,1:18:23.00,1:18:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还是想要做呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:18:28.20,1:18:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要更多了...
Dialogue: 2,1:18:31.67,1:18:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}更多！
Dialogue: 2,1:18:47.52,1:18:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢我一边舔，一边摸乳头吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:18:59.64,1:19:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这样会很兴奋吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:19:28.55,1:19:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}舒服吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:19:31.72,1:19:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真棒，看你满足的样子！
Dialogue: 2,1:19:55.70,1:19:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你真是个变态啊
Dialogue: 2,1:20:16.77,1:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要我更用力吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:20:30.57,1:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真棒的表情啊
Dialogue: 2,1:21:08.83,1:21:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没有人能做的比我更好哦
Dialogue: 2,1:21:17.52,1:21:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我真的很讨厌它！
Dialogue: 2,1:21:22.75,1:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你好像很喜欢我拍它？
Dialogue: 2,1:21:31.12,1:21:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你感觉很舒服？
Dialogue: 2,1:21:33.80,1:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你真是个变态啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:21:41.52,1:21:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你很喜欢被欺负吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:21:48.50,1:21:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}现在...
Dialogue: 2,1:21:50.37,1:21:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}给我忍住！
Dialogue: 2,1:21:52.95,1:21:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要有耐心哦
Dialogue: 2,1:22:25.92,1:22:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}肉棒的味道好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:23:02.83,1:23:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不能这么做！
Dialogue: 2,1:23:05.12,1:23:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我还没好好品尝美味的肉棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:23:09.95,1:23:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么？你的肉棒很舒服吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:23:24.87,1:23:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我感觉你好像很难受
Dialogue: 2,1:23:28.55,1:23:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就让你更兴奋吧
Dialogue: 2,1:23:41.02,1:23:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}舒服吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:23:43.92,1:23:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这样会很兴奋吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:23:49.15,1:23:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要我饶了你吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:23:55.57,1:23:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快点乞求我原谅你
Dialogue: 2,1:24:02.32,1:24:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还是？你喜欢这样?
Dialogue: 2,1:24:14.95,1:24:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的乳头现在很硬哦
Dialogue: 2,1:24:19.60,1:24:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真是个变态啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:24:24.60,1:24:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这样乳头很兴奋吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:24:32.30,1:24:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很舒服吧
Dialogue: 2,1:24:43.47,1:24:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我们做更多兴奋的事情吧
Dialogue: 2,1:24:53.66,1:24:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你现在的表情好像很辛苦
Dialogue: 2,1:25:00.97,1:25:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你真的很饥渴哦
Dialogue: 2,1:25:07.33,1:25:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你喜欢这样，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:25:15.72,1:25:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乳头…
Dialogue: 2,1:25:20.05,1:25:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的乳头好硬哦
Dialogue: 2,1:25:23.15,1:25:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒的表情哦
Dialogue: 2,1:25:33.05,1:25:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒
Dialogue: 2,1:25:37.37,1:25:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,1:25:45.72,1:25:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你没有其他选择哦
Dialogue: 2,1:25:54.70,1:25:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我很有耐心哦
Dialogue: 2,1:25:58.15,1:26:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你好能忍受哦
Dialogue: 2,1:26:04.33,1:26:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要坚持住哦
Dialogue: 2,1:26:10.17,1:26:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不行，不能射！
Dialogue: 2,1:26:14.67,1:26:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不行！
Dialogue: 2,1:26:17.52,1:26:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不准射！
Dialogue: 2,1:26:20.50,1:26:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忍住！明白吗?
Dialogue: 2,1:26:23.65,1:26:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你听到了吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:26:29.87,1:26:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果你忍住，可以得到我的奖励哦。
Dialogue: 2,1:26:51.85,1:26:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你做的很好哦
Dialogue: 2,1:27:00.35,1:27:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道有什么奖励吧
Dialogue: 2,1:27:21.85,1:27:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道我最喜欢什么吗?
Dialogue: 2,1:27:25.72,1:27:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我喜欢色情
Dialogue: 2,1:27:32.20,1:27:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就是现在正在做的
Dialogue: 2,1:27:51.17,1:27:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你很舒服吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:28:10.77,1:28:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你可以射出来哦
Dialogue: 2,1:28:33.87,1:28:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要射了吗？   好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:28:37.25,1:28:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会让你感觉更好哦
Dialogue: 2,1:28:40.65,1:28:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}知道吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:28:43.02,1:28:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还有吗？还有的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:28:45.12,1:28:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很爽吧？还能射的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:28:48.25,1:28:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:28:52.90,1:28:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒啊！出来了吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:28:55.82,1:28:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再射出来！
Dialogue: 2,1:29:00.90,1:29:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}出来了吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:29:05.47,1:29:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等等...再坚持一下下哦
Dialogue: 2,1:29:18.25,1:29:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很爽，很舒服吧！
Dialogue: 2,1:29:26.10,1:29:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要来了吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:29:36.84,1:29:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:29:38.35,1:29:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快一点！
Dialogue: 2,1:29:47.45,1:29:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊！好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:30:16.37,1:30:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真的射了好多啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:30:23.00,1:30:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}感觉很爽吧?
Dialogue: 2,1:30:29.55,1:30:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我说...
Dialogue: 2,1:30:31.75,1:30:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}下次你能让我舒服的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:30:44.87,1:30:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那么...
Dialogue: 2,1:30:47.52,1:30:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}现在要麻烦你咯！
Dialogue: 2,1:31:02.25,1:31:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你还能射出来的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:31:08.16,1:31:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}知道啦！
Dialogue: 2,1:31:10.87,1:31:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再做一次咯
Dialogue: 2,1:31:38.72,1:31:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}舌头好软哦
Dialogue: 2,1:32:04.87,1:32:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很想要的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:32:27.72,1:32:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很想要吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:32:37.80,1:32:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乳头变得好硬了
Dialogue: 2,1:32:50.95,1:32:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这次...你的肉棒能射多少存货给我呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:32:59.00,1:33:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小南的胸让你觉得舒服吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:33:01.97,1:33:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}它很热吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:33:53.15,1:33:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天我有足够的耐心哦
Dialogue: 2,1:34:20.17,1:34:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒！肉棒好大哦！大到让我吃惊了！
Dialogue: 2,1:34:43.16,1:34:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这个肉棒感觉好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:35:07.33,1:35:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}肉棒变得好可爱啊
Dialogue: 2,1:35:12.60,1:35:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看吧...
Dialogue: 2,1:35:15.16,1:35:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}它看起来不错哦，感觉好棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:35:25.67,1:35:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}屁股很棒吧
Dialogue: 2,1:35:40.33,1:35:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我看起来是不是很棒啊？
Dialogue: 2,1:35:50.15,1:35:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就是这样！
Dialogue: 2,1:36:01.32,1:36:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}继续哦，玩弄我的小穴。
Dialogue: 2,1:36:10.32,1:36:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快让我的小穴吃饱！让我更舒服！
Dialogue: 2,1:36:28.87,1:36:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:36:32.75,1:36:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}感觉好舒服啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:36:44.17,1:36:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去了！
Dialogue: 2,1:36:50.12,1:36:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}感觉好爽啊！更多...我要肉棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:36:54.92,1:36:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要肉棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:37:16.15,1:37:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这个肉棒感觉好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:37:21.02,1:37:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你在看肉棒插小穴的样子吧
Dialogue: 2,1:37:36.67,1:37:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好爽啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:37:55.02,1:37:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去了！
Dialogue: 2,1:37:58.35,1:38:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要去了！
Dialogue: 2,1:38:14.55,1:38:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这鸡巴好硬啊！感觉太舒服了！更多...
Dialogue: 2,1:38:20.30,1:38:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还要更多！
Dialogue: 2,1:38:21.94,1:38:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}感觉太棒了！
Dialogue: 2,1:38:34.07,1:38:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你喜欢看小南的乳头，对吧?
Dialogue: 2,1:38:53.12,1:38:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好爽啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:38:59.12,1:39:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}肉棒在慢慢加速哦
Dialogue: 2,1:39:06.33,1:39:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看到了吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:39:32.30,1:39:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}更多...
Dialogue: 2,1:39:33.87,1:39:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要更多！快操我！
Dialogue: 2,1:39:37.00,1:39:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快从后面用肉棒操我！
Dialogue: 2,1:39:49.12,1:39:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}从后面操我!
Dialogue: 2,1:40:07.65,1:40:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:40:10.80,1:40:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快点操我！我好喜欢！
Dialogue: 2,1:40:35.58,1:40:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不行了
Dialogue: 2,1:40:41.05,1:40:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要去了！
Dialogue: 2,1:40:52.27,1:40:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒啊！太爽了！
Dialogue: 2,1:41:11.15,1:41:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小穴好饱...好饱！好爽！小穴爽死了！
Dialogue: 2,1:41:42.50,1:41:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你好厉害哦!
Dialogue: 2,1:41:54.25,1:41:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}更多...
Dialogue: 2,1:41:55.64,1:41:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要更多！
Dialogue: 2,1:41:57.49,1:42:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}插深一点...再插深一点！
Dialogue: 2,1:42:13.45,1:42:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就是这样！就是这样！
Dialogue: 2,1:42:27.50,1:42:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:42:47.22,1:42:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:43:00.32,1:43:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}肉棒越来越大，越来越硬了!
Dialogue: 2,1:43:12.82,1:43:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为什么停下啊？
Dialogue: 2,1:43:15.75,1:43:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}肉棒不行了吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:43:20.17,1:43:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你可以继续操我哦
Dialogue: 2,1:43:31.70,1:43:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快看我，看我淫荡的样子！
Dialogue: 2,1:44:03.17,1:44:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好舒服，好舒服啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:44:05.50,1:44:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}更多...快给我更多！
Dialogue: 2,1:45:00.92,1:45:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你还想再做一次吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:45:18.07,1:45:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你可以再做一次的吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:45:20.72,1:45:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等等...不行了...
Dialogue: 2,1:45:24.90,1:45:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快来做吧！
Dialogue: 2,1:45:30.32,1:45:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快把肉棒放到小穴里
Dialogue: 2,1:45:33.16,1:45:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}可以再来一次哦
Dialogue: 2,1:45:44.17,1:45:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快点...好想要！
Dialogue: 2,1:46:08.80,1:46:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快给我...更多...给我更多！
Dialogue: 2,1:46:33.25,1:46:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒！好舒服！
Dialogue: 2,1:46:43.82,1:46:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去了.......
Dialogue: 2,1:47:17.50,1:47:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}站起来...站起来操我
Dialogue: 2,1:47:55.87,1:48:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}给我更多...更多！
Dialogue: 2,1:48:16.00,1:48:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:48:17.42,1:48:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}更多...
Dialogue: 2,1:48:41.35,1:48:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒...好棒...给我更多！
Dialogue: 2,1:48:46.55,1:48:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去了......
Dialogue: 2,1:49:02.92,1:49:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}更多...继续操我！
Dialogue: 2,1:49:35.62,1:49:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好舒服！
Dialogue: 2,1:50:02.85,1:50:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒！
Dialogue: 2,1:50:04.66,1:50:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}更多...快喂饱我！我好喜欢...
Dialogue: 2,1:50:39.20,1:50:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这样来操我！
Dialogue: 2,1:51:53.90,1:51:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊！好棒啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:52:28.10,1:52:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快点...快点射给我！
Dialogue: 2,1:52:55.57,1:52:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}射了！
Dialogue: 2,1:52:56.85,1:52:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}射到我脸上！
Dialogue: 2,1:53:06.10,1:53:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好棒！好多啊！
Dialogue: 2,1:53:33.77,1:53:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不行了...我受不了了！
Dialogue: 2,1:53:48.30,1:53:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还能再来一次吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:53:53.97,1:53:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我还想要...更多！
Dialogue: 2,1:54:04.00,1:54:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我的生活太棒了！
